{"tid":1717811,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"一青年在荃灣不幸身亡各位請默哀","createTime":"2019-11-13T16:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T06:16:40.000Z","uid":29928,"like":125,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"13d5b7d4b2d23654ede2cca2e01bd53af38bd926","tid":1717811,"uid":29928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16:44:46.000Z","msg":"深夜10時許，有人途經荃灣嘉里物流中心對開，發現一名身穿黑衣、黑褲的青年，倒臥在地面浴血，昏迷不醒，立即報案求助。救護員趕到現場，為傷者作初步檢查，發現他身體多處受傷，需急送就近的仁濟醫院，經搶救後延至深夜約11時許證實不治。<br />\n<br />\n#新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/447574042745438/permalink/547029712799870?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F447574042745438%2Fpermalink%2F547029712799870%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4ey3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=6d5d26fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/447574042745438/permalink/547029712799870?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n我收到一個壞消息，岩岩係嘉里貨運中心，有一個年輕著黑衣褲，畀人掉落樓，呢單野係的士朋友睇到，現場無新聞記者 ，請記者去瑪嘉烈醫院去睇下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Tonyworld15/status/1194633108156403714?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTonyworld15%2Fstatus%2F1194633108156403714%3Fs%3D20&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4ey3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=d93e2a4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTonyworld15%2Fstatus%2F1194633108156403714%3Fs%3D20&h=c81852f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Tonyworld15/status/1194633108156403714?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\nFrom tg<br />\n最早目擊者時間為2233<br />\n被發現係葵福路 嘉里物流外<br />\n無心跳 做緊cpr 同aed <br />\n手有復習性骨折<br />\n已上白車<br />\n白車車牌 a137<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nFA 指無目擊者<br />\n但佢有急救牌 <br />\n睇骨折程度 似高處跌下 更似被斬<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">荃灣</span></span>"},{"pid":"a0dab2e24e9cf009b023ca0d9856484acbb75ef7","tid":1717811,"uid":326463,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T16: